OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,FAround 20% of women will experience
OL,8,Fmental health struggles in pregnancy
OL,9,For after birth.
OL,11,FA small number will get so severely
OL,12,Fill, they need to be admitted to a
OL,13,Fpsychiatric unit like this.
OL,15,FIt's calmer and quieter than a general
OL,16,Fadult psychiatric ward, except for the
OL,17,Fgentle murmurs of newborn babies being
OL,18,Fcomforted by specialist staff.
