OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,FPerinatal Consultant Nurse, Stef
OL,8,FMaudsley, says society puts pressure
OL,9,Fon mothers to be the "perfect mum" and
OL,10,Fto enjoy parenthood from the outset.
OL,12,F"For lots of people that's just not
OL,13,Fthe experience, it can be very
OL,14,Fdifficult to adapt to being a parent
OL,15,Fand very lonely."
OL,17,FSix years ago, Ribblemere Mother and
OL,18,FBaby Unit did not exist, so women in
OL,19,Fthis part of Lancashire would have had
OL,20,Fto travel miles or go to a general
OL,21,Fadult psychiatric ward.
