OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,FHis death left Kath in crisis and, say
OL,8,Fher family, a chasm of care.
OL,10,F"The services just weren't there to
OL,11,Fsupport someone like Kath," her sister-
OL,12,Fin-law Rose James told ITV News.
OL,14,FSeven months after the death her son,
OL,15,FKath died by suicide.
OL,17,F"She just slipped through the net.
OL,18,FThere should be somewhere for bereaved
OL,19,Ffamilies to seek help."
