OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,FThe psychiatric hospital where Kath
OL,8,Fwas being treated allowed her to leave
OL,9,Funescorted, despite two previous
OL,10,Fsuicide attempts.
OL,12,F"We've lost the heart of the family.
OL,13,FEven 18 months on we fully expect her
OL,14,Fto walk through the door and she is
OL,15,Fnever going to. It has just devastated
OL,16,Four family completely," said Rosie.
OL,18,FAn inquest found failings at the
OL,19,Fhospital contributed to her death.
