OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,FNHS England says every part of England
OL,8,Fnow has a specialist mental health
OL,9,Fteam offering women with moderate to
OL,10,Fsevere or complex mental health needs
OL,11,Fsupport.
OL,13,FBut experts say despite the increase
OL,14,Fin services in recent years, staff
OL,15,Fshortages and unstable funding are
OL,16,Fhampering efforts.
OL,18,F"There's huge demand for care and
OL,19,Fservices," says Dr Livia Martucci from
OL,20,Fthe Royal College of Psychiatrists.
