OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,F"Even though services have expanded,
OL,8,Fthey are stretched. And sometimes they
OL,9,Fstruggle to meet demand."
OL,11,FHealth minister, Maria Caulfield, told
OL,12,FITV News the government is "committed
OL,13,Fto ensuring these services are
OL,14,Favailable to every new mother who
OL,15,Fneeds them, no matter where they live
OL,16,Fin England."
OL,18,FShe continued: "The government has
OL,19,Falso significantly increased spending
OL,20,Fon mental health to support these
OL,21,Fambitions."
